<h3 id="PrimLite">Primary Literature</h3>

<p>
For the convenience of the internet reader, citations from classical
texts are referenced to the chapter and paragraph number in
 <a href="https://ctext.org/">Online Original https://ctext.org</a>.
 Translations of the <em>Zhuangzi</em> in this article are those of
its author. A public domain translation accompanies the Online
Original on the site and the reader can easily access a
character-by-character standard dictionary translation of the passages
by clicking the blue &ldquo;jump to dictionary&rdquo; icon. Other
tranlsations of the <em>Zhuangzi </em>include:</p>

<ul class="hanging">

<li>Graham, Angus C. (trans.), 1981, <em>Chuang-tz&#365;: The Seven
Inner Chapters and Other Writings from the Book Chuang-tz&#365;</em>,
Boston: Allen and Unwin.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash; (trans.), 1981, <em>Chuang Tz&#365;: The
Inner Chapters</em>, London: Hackett Publishing Co. Inc.</li>

